37
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:04,280
The combination cosine theta plus i sine

38
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:09,160
theta is called e to the i theta.

39
00:02:09,160 --> 00:02:12,180
e to the power i theta.

40
00:02:12,180 --> 00:02:15,080
So know that definition.

41
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:19,680
e to the i theta is

42
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:24,280
cosine theta plus i sine theta.

43
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:27,780
The reason we call it e to the i

44
00:02:27,780 --> 00:02:31,280
theta is because it satisfies certain rules of exponentials.

45
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:34,780
The rules of exponentials is that when

46
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:38,280
you multiply exponentials, you add the exponents.

