00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:54,780
and you write e to the i phi, which

52
00:02:54,780 --> 00:02:59,280
is cosine phi plus i sine phi, and multiply them,

53
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:03,280
you get something with a real and an imaginary part.

54
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:05,780
The real part is cosine theta cosine

55
00:03:05,780 --> 00:03:08,280
phi minus sine theta times sine phi.

